{
  "info": {
    "name": "Pookie Style — AI Product Creator v2",
    "description": "Test collection for the Pookie Style AI Product Creation backend.\n\nEndpoint: https://asia-south1-pookie-style-automation.cloudfunctions.net/create-product\n\nTotal API calls per product: 3 (1 OpenAI + 2 Replicate)\nTotal images uploaded to Shopify: 2 (hero + collage)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "backend_url",
      "value": "https://asia-south1-pookie-style-automation.cloudfunctions.net/create-product",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health Check",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Health Check — Empty POST (should return 400)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": ""
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{backend_url}}",
              "host": ["{{backend_url}}"]
            },
            "description": "Quick health check. Sends empty POST — backend should respond with:\n{\n  \"error\": \"No images uploaded. At least 1 image is required.\"\n}\n\nHTTP 400 = Backend is ALIVE and validating correctly."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Backend is alive (returns 400 for empty request)', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(400);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Returns correct validation error', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.error).to.include('No images uploaded');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "2. CORS Preflight — OPTIONS (should return 204)",
          "request": {
            "method": "OPTIONS",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Origin", "value": "https://pookiestyle.in" },
              { "key": "Access-Control-Request-Method", "value": "POST" },
              { "key": "Access-Control-Request-Headers", "value": "Content-Type" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{backend_url}}",
              "host": ["{{backend_url}}"]
            },
            "description": "Tests CORS preflight. Should return 204 with:\n- Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *\n- Access-Control-Allow-Methods: POST, OPTIONS"
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('CORS preflight returns 204', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(204);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('CORS headers present', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.header('Access-Control-Allow-Origin');",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.header('Access-Control-Allow-Methods');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Validation Tests",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "3. Missing Price (should return 400)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "images",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": "",
                  "description": "⬆️ SELECT A GARMENT IMAGE FILE HERE"
                },
                { "key": "sizes", "value": "M,L", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{backend_url}}",
              "host": ["{{backend_url}}"]
            },
            "description": "Tests validation: price and compare_at_price are required.\nShould return 400 with error message."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Returns 400 for missing price', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(400);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Error mentions price', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.error).to.include('Price');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Missing Sizes (should return 400)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "images",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": "",
                  "description": "⬆️ SELECT A GARMENT IMAGE FILE HERE"
                },
                { "key": "price", "value": "599", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "compare_at_price", "value": "999", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{backend_url}}",
              "host": ["{{backend_url}}"]
            },
            "description": "Tests validation: sizes field is required.\nShould return 400 with error message."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Returns 400 for missing sizes', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(400);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Error mentions size', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.error).to.include('size');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Product Creation",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "5. ⭐ Create Product — Minimal (AI generates everything)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "images",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": "",
                  "description": "⬆️ SELECT A GARMENT IMAGE FILE HERE (JPG/PNG, max 10MB)"
                },
                { "key": "price", "value": "599", "type": "text", "description": "Selling price in ₹" },
                { "key": "compare_at_price", "value": "999", "type": "text", "description": "Original/compare price in ₹" },
                { "key": "sizes", "value": "M,L,XL", "type": "text", "description": "Comma-separated sizes" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{backend_url}}",
              "host": ["{{backend_url}}"]
            },
            "description": "MINIMAL product creation — only required fields.\nAI will auto-generate: product name, description, tags, SEO, category.\n\n⏱️ Takes ~60-90 seconds (3 API calls).\n\n✅ Expected: Product created as DRAFT in Shopify."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Returns 200 success', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Product created successfully', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.product_name).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.product_url).to.include('pookiestyle.in');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.admin_url).to.include('myshopify.com');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Images uploaded', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.images_uploaded).to.be.at.least(1);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Tags generated (35-50)', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.tags_count).to.be.at.least(35);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Dress style detected', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    var validStyles = ['traditional', 'western', 'fusion', 'formal'];",
                  "    pm.expect(validStyles).to.include(json.dress_style);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "// Save product URL for later",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('last_product_url', json.product_url);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('last_admin_url', json.admin_url);",
                  "    console.log('Product created: ' + json.product_name);",
                  "    console.log('Admin URL: ' + json.admin_url);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "6. ⭐ Create Product — Full (all fields)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "images",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": "",
                  "description": "⬆️ SELECT A GARMENT IMAGE FILE HERE (JPG/PNG, max 10MB)"
                },
                { "key": "price", "value": "799", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "compare_at_price", "value": "1499", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "sizes", "value": "S,M,L,XL,XXL", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "name", "value": "Emerald Green Embroidered A-Line Kurti", "type": "text", "description": "Custom product name (overrides AI)" },
                { "key": "description", "value": "Pure cotton fabric, lightweight and breathable. Perfect for daily and office wear.", "type": "text", "description": "Notes for AI to include in description" },
                { "key": "category", "value": "kurti", "type": "text", "description": "Shopify collection handle" },
                { "key": "extra_prompt", "value": "Show with traditional Indian poses, warm festive background", "type": "text", "description": "Custom styling instruction for image generation" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{backend_url}}",
              "host": ["{{backend_url}}"]
            },
            "description": "FULL product creation — all fields including optional ones.\n\nFields:\n- images: garment photo (required)\n- price: selling price (required)\n- compare_at_price: original price (required)\n- sizes: comma-separated (required)\n- name: custom product name (optional)\n- description: notes for AI (optional)\n- category: collection handle (optional)\n- extra_prompt: custom styling (optional, NEW in v2)\n\n⏱️ Takes ~60-90 seconds.\n\n✅ Expected: Product created as DRAFT with custom name."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Returns 200 success', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Product created with custom name', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.product_name).to.equal('Emerald Green Embroidered A-Line Kurti');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Collection assigned', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.collections_assigned).to.include('kurti');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('AI analysis returned', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.ai_analysis).to.be.an('object');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.ai_analysis.garment_type).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.ai_analysis.dress_style).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "7. ⭐ Create Product — Western Dress",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "images",
